 "and then ",
 StyleBox["Copy/Paste",
  FontWeight->"Bold",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 StyleBox["d the output into this notebook into the sentence where you found \
it. ",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
